{"tid":704168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有相慎入)基金公司CEO只穿內褲被燒死　疑電話充電爆炸","createTime":"2018-06-16T08:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T09:06:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"71f6c9a617ce0b60f7585a4835672e84295069c4","tid":704168,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:53:49.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180616/640_9b9cd790aaf253c1d73c66e76c0c9b97.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180616%2F640_9b9cd790aaf253c1d73c66e76c0c9b97.jpg&d=pf22FSXlZHl%2F3nQR5BVjv1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=b3fdde4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180616/640_9b9cd790aaf253c1d73c66e76c0c9b97.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n馬來西亞一名基金公司總執行長納茲林，在14日中午被發現於家中被燒死，死時僅穿一條內褲。家屬懷疑，可能是納茲林的電話在充電時爆炸起火，燒死正在睡午覺的納茲林。<br />\n<br />\n據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，納茲林是搖籃私人基金公司(Cradle Fund Sdn Bhd)的CEO，不過在14日中午左右，納茲林的家中突然起火，火勢撲滅後，警消也在屋內發現納茲林的遺體。報導指出，納茲林被發現時身上僅穿內褲，被燒死在屋內，而納茲林的妻子和4名孩子則及時逃生。<br />\n<br />\n家屬指出，案發當時納茲林正在睡午覺，懷疑是電話充電爆炸釀悲劇，也導致納茲林後腦勺嚴重灼傷，隨後更燒到納茲林的床鋪。家屬也指出，納茲林是3C愛好者，擁有黑莓和<span style=\"color: red;\">華為</span>兩個品牌的智慧型電話，目前家屬不排除是電話充電釀禍，但並不確定是哪支電話充電出問題。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180616/1374348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180616%2F1374348&d=pf22FSXlZHl%2F3nQR5BVjv1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=6ebeff87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180616%2F1374348&h=de599325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180616/1374348</a>"},{"pid":"ec36afa9fe85f3079d5664d9fcb0ed2b8fd6e025","tid":704168,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"華為 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}